name: Odyssey
description:
The first collab between The Timeless Room and Cavernicollage.

This is a collage window to "2001: A Space Odyssey" a gem that never stop to inspire new universes.

So here we are, following the signs of an ancient monolith on the moon. "My God, it's full of stars!" Art is a guide, an amulet and an adventure in the journey of friendship.
